<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>ECOFLOW by Sa Systems — Environmental Operations Platform</title>
<meta name="description" content="ECOFLOW is the end-to-end environmental operations platform by Sa Systems — collection, routing, fleet, recycling, compliance, subscriptions and reporting in one Odoo-native suite." />
<style>
  :root {
    --green: #16a34a;
    --green-600: #15803d;
    --blue: #0ea5e9;
    --ink: #0b1220;
    --slate: #64748b;
    --slate-200: #e2e8f0;
    --surface: #f8fafc;
    --amber: #f59e0b;
    --radius: 18px;
    --maxw: 1140px;
    --ease: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    --text-hero: clamp(2.6rem, 1.2rem + 5vw, 5rem);
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: #fff;
    line-height: 1.55;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }
  a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
  .wrap { max-width: var(--maxw); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }

  /* ---------- Nav ---------- */
  header.nav {
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50;
    backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(14px);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-200);
  }
  .nav-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; height: 72px; }
  .brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .brand img { height: 40px; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 28px; align-items: center; }
  .nav-links a { color: var(--slate); font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: color 0.2s var(--ease); }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    padding: 12px 22px; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s var(--ease), box-shadow 0.2s var(--ease), background 0.2s var(--ease);
    cursor: pointer; border: 0;
  }
  .btn-primary { background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--green), var(--blue)); color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.28); }
  .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.38); }
  .btn-ghost { background: #fff; color: var(--ink); border: 1px solid var(--slate-200); }
  .btn-ghost:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); border-color: var(--green); }

  /* ---------- Hero ---------- */
  .hero { position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 96px 0 64px; }
  .hero::before {
    content: ""; position: absolute; inset: -40% 30% auto -20%; height: 700px;
    background: radial-gradient(closest-side, rgba(22,163,74,0.18), transparent);
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .hero::after {
    content: ""; position: absolute; inset: -10% -20% auto 40%; height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(closest-side, rgba(14,165,233,0.16), transparent);
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .hero .wrap { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    padding: 7px 14px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(22,163,74,0.1);
    color: var(--green-600); font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .eyebrow .dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--green); box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(22,163,74,0.18); }
  h1.hero-title {
    font-size: var(--text-hero); line-height: 1.02; margin: 0 0 18px;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em; font-weight: 800; max-width: 14ch;
  }
  h1.hero-title .grad { background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--green), var(--blue)); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; color: transparent; }
  .hero p.lead { font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 0.96rem + 0.5vw, 1.3rem); color: var(--slate); max-width: 58ch; margin: 0 0 32px; }
  .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .hero-stats { display: flex; gap: 40px; margin-top: 52px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .hero-stats .stat strong { display: block; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .hero-stats .stat span { color: var(--slate); font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; }

  /* ---------- Section ---------- */
  section { padding: 84px 0; }
  .section-head { max-width: 64ch; margin: 0 auto 52px; text-align: center; }
  .section-head .kicker { color: var(--green-600); font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; font-size: 0.82rem; }
  .section-head h2 { font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 1.2rem + 2.2vw, 3rem); margin: 12px 0 14px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .section-head p { color: var(--slate); font-size: 1.08rem; }

  /* ---------- Capability bento ---------- */
  .bento { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
  .card {
    background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--slate-200); border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 28px; transition: transform 0.25s var(--ease), box-shadow 0.25s var(--ease), border-color 0.25s var(--ease);
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(11,18,32,0.1); border-color: transparent; }
  .card .ic { width: 46px; height: 46px; border-radius: 12px; display: grid; place-items: center; font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #fff; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green), var(--blue)); }
  .card h3 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 1.2rem; }
  .card p { margin: 0; color: var(--slate); font-size: 0.96rem; }
  .card.span-3 { grid-column: span 3; }
  .card.span-2 { grid-column: span 2; }
  .card.feature { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0b1220, #11203a); color: #fff; }
  .card.feature h3 { color: #fff; }
  .card.feature p { color: #cbd5e1; }
  .card .tag-list { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 16px; }
  .card .tag { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 5px 11px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(22,163,74,0.12); color: var(--green-600); }
  .card.feature .tag { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: #e2e8f0; }

  /* ---------- Product preview ---------- */
  .preview .shot { margin: 0; border-radius: 20px; padding: 14px; background: linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(22,163,74,0.10), rgba(14,165,233,0.10)); border: 1px solid var(--slate-200); box-shadow: 0 30px 70px rgba(15,23,42,0.14); }
  .preview .shot img { display: block; width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--slate-200); }

  /* ---------- Metric band ---------- */
  .band { background: var(--surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--slate-200); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-200); }
  .metric-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
  .metric { text-align: center; }
  .metric strong { display: block; font-size: 2.6rem; font-weight: 800; background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--green), var(--blue)); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; color: transparent; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .metric span { color: var(--slate); font-weight: 600; }

  /* ---------- Workflow ---------- */
  .flow { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 14px; counter-reset: step; }
  .flow .step { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--slate-200); border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px 18px; position: relative; }
  .flow .step::before { counter-increment: step; content: "0" counter(step); font-weight: 800; color: var(--green); font-size: 1.4rem; }
  .flow .step h4 { margin: 8px 0 6px; font-size: 1.02rem; }
  .flow .step p { margin: 0; color: var(--slate); font-size: 0.88rem; }

  /* ---------- Pricing ---------- */
  .pricing { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 22px; align-items: stretch; }
  .plan { border: 1px solid var(--slate-200); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 32px; background: #fff; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .plan.popular { border: 2px solid var(--green); box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(22,163,74,0.16); position: relative; }
  .plan.popular .badge { position: absolute; top: -14px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--green), var(--blue)); color: #fff; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
  .plan h3 { margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 1.3rem; }
  .plan .price { font-size: 2.6rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 10px 0 4px; }
  .plan .price small { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--slate); font-weight: 600; }
  .plan ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 20px 0 26px; display: grid; gap: 11px; }
  .plan li { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; color: var(--slate); font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .plan li::before { content: "✓"; color: var(--green); font-weight: 800; }
  .plan .btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; margin-top: auto; }

  /* ---------- CTA ---------- */
  .cta-final { background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--green), var(--blue)); color: #fff; border-radius: 28px; padding: 64px 40px; text-align: center; }
  .cta-final h2 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 1.3rem + 2.4vw, 3.2rem); margin: 0 0 12px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .cta-final p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92); font-size: 1.15rem; max-width: 56ch; margin: 0 auto 28px; }
  .cta-final .btn-ghost { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14); color: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }
  .cta-final .btn-white { background: #fff; color: var(--green-600); }

  /* ---------- Footer ---------- */
  footer { padding: 48px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--slate-200); color: var(--slate); }
  .foot-inner { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px; }
  .foot-inner img { height: 34px; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .bento { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .card.span-3, .card.span-2 { grid-column: span 2; }
    .metric-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .flow { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .pricing { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="nav">
  <div class="wrap nav-inner">
    <div class="brand"><img src="assets/sa_systems_logo.png" alt="Sa Systems" /></div>
    <nav class="nav-links">
      <a href="#capabilities">Capabilities</a>
      <a href="#workflow">Workflow</a>
      <a href="#outcomes">Outcomes</a>
      <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
    </nav>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#pricing">Request a Demo</a>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span> ECOFLOW · Environmental Operations Platform</span>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Run waste &amp; recycling operations on <span class="grad">one intelligent platform</span></h1>
    <p class="lead">ECOFLOW by Sa Systems unifies collection, routing, fleet, recycling, compliance, customer subscriptions and reporting — Odoo-native, audit-ready, and engineered for operational efficiency.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#pricing">Start Free Trial</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#capabilities">Explore Capabilities →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat"><strong>7</strong><span>Operational modules</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><strong>+30%</strong><span>Route efficiency</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><strong>100%</strong><span>Chain-of-custody</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><strong>18 / 19</strong><span>Odoo compatible</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="preview" class="preview">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="kicker">Live Cockpit</span>
      <h2>Your operation, at a glance</h2>
      <p>A real-time KPI cockpit surfaces collections, recovery and compliance the moment your crews report from the field.</p>
    </div>
    <figure class="shot">
      <img src="assets/demo_cockpit.png" alt="ECOFLOW Operations Cockpit dashboard showing today's collections, recovery and diversion, and compliance KPIs" loading="lazy" width="1480" height="1020" />
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="capabilities">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="kicker">Capabilities</span>
      <h2>Everything from kerbside to compliance</h2>
      <p>A connected operating system for environmental services — each capability feeds the next, with a single source of truth.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bento">
      <div class="card feature span-3">
        <div class="ic">♻️</div>
        <h3>Smart Collection</h3>
        <p>Bin registries, RFID/QR proof-of-service, fill-level capture and service orders that turn the field into structured, billable data.</p>
        <div class="tag-list"><span class="tag">RFID / QR</span><span class="tag">Proof of service</span><span class="tag">Fill levels</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card span-3">
        <div class="ic">🗺️</div>
        <h3>Route Optimization</h3>
        <p>Nearest-neighbour route building, depot anchoring and live dispatch that cut distance, fuel and overtime.</p>
        <div class="tag-list"><span class="tag">Auto-optimize</span><span class="tag">Dispatch</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card span-2">
        <div class="ic">🚛</div>
        <h3>Fleet</h3>
        <p>Vehicles, drivers and assignments integrated through Odoo Fleet.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card span-2">
        <div class="ic">🏭</div>
        <h3>Recycling &amp; Recovery</h3>
        <p>Weighbridge tickets, MRF process batches, mass-balance validation and diversion yield.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card span-2">
        <div class="ic">📋</div>
        <h3>Compliance</h3>
        <p>Digital manifests with a signature chain, permit lifecycle alerts and waste codes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card span-3">
        <div class="ic">💳</div>
        <h3>Customer Subscriptions</h3>
        <p>Service sites, recurring plans and billing methods — flat, per-lift or by weight — ready for invoicing.</p>
        <div class="tag-list"><span class="tag">Flat</span><span class="tag">Per-lift</span><span class="tag">By weight</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card span-3">
        <div class="ic">📊</div>
        <h3>Dashboards &amp; Reporting</h3>
        <p>An operations cockpit with live KPIs plus graph &amp; pivot analysis across every stage of the value chain.</p>
        <div class="tag-list"><span class="tag">Live cockpit</span><span class="tag">Graph</span><span class="tag">Pivot</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="workflow" class="band">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="kicker">Workflow</span>
      <h2>One continuous operational flow</h2>
      <p>Every action is captured once and flows downstream — no double entry, no broken chain of custody.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flow">
      <div class="step"><h4>Schedule</h4><p>Generate service orders from subscriptions &amp; sites.</p></div>
      <div class="step"><h4>Route</h4><p>Optimize and dispatch routes to fleet &amp; drivers.</p></div>
      <div class="step"><h4>Service</h4><p>Capture proof-of-service, weights &amp; photos in the field.</p></div>
      <div class="step"><h4>Recover</h4><p>Weigh, process and validate diversion at the facility.</p></div>
      <div class="step"><h4>Report</h4><p>Close manifests and surface KPIs to managers.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="outcomes">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="kicker">Outcomes</span>
      <h2>Measurable operational efficiency</h2>
      <p>ECOFLOW is built around an Operational Efficiency Index — the north-star metric for environmental services.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-grid">
      <div class="metric"><strong>-22%</strong><span>Cost per lift</span></div>
      <div class="metric"><strong>+18%</strong><span>Diversion rate</span></div>
      <div class="metric"><strong>99.5%</strong><span>Manifest accuracy</span></div>
      <div class="metric"><strong>4.6h</strong><span>Saved per route/week</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="pricing" class="band">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="kicker">Pricing</span>
      <h2>Plans that scale with your fleet</h2>
      <p>Transparent per-vehicle pricing. Self-host on Odoo 18 or 19, or let Sa Systems run it for you.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pricing">
      <div class="plan">
        <h3>Starter</h3>
        <div class="price">$0<small> / community</small></div>
        <p style="color:var(--slate); margin:0;">Self-hosted, open-source modules.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>All 6 ECOFLOW modules</li>
          <li>Collection, routing &amp; recycling</li>
          <li>Operations cockpit</li>
          <li>Community support</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#">Download</a>
      </div>
      <div class="plan popular">
        <span class="badge">Most Popular</span>
        <h3>Operator</h3>
        <div class="price">$29<small> / vehicle / mo</small></div>
        <p style="color:var(--slate); margin:0;">Managed cloud with onboarding.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Everything in Starter</li>
          <li>Managed hosting &amp; backups</li>
          <li>Compliance &amp; manifest automation</li>
          <li>Subscription billing</li>
          <li>Priority support &amp; SLAs</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">Request a Demo</a>
      </div>
      <div class="plan">
        <h3>Enterprise</h3>
        <div class="price">Custom</div>
        <p style="color:var(--slate); margin:0;">For multi-depot networks.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Everything in Operator</li>
          <li>Telematics &amp; IoT integrations</li>
          <li>Custom dashboards &amp; APIs</li>
          <li>Dedicated success manager</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#">Talk to Sales</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="cta-final">
      <h2>Bring your operations into flow</h2>
      <p>See ECOFLOW running on your data. Book a live walkthrough with the Sa Systems team and get a tailored efficiency assessment.</p>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:14px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a class="btn btn-white" href="#">Request a Demo</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#capabilities">View Capabilities</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="wrap foot-inner">
    <img src="assets/sa_systems_logo.png" alt="Sa Systems" />
    <span>© 2025 Sa Systems · ECOFLOW Environmental Operations Platform</span>
    <span>Odoo 18 / 19 · LGPL-3</span>
  </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
